## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent and comprehensive studies specifically focused on the reasons behind reading negative comments. The findings are based on a selection of articles and may not encompass all possible psychological and social factors. Additionally, the dynamic nature of online interactions means that motivations can vary widely among different individuals and contexts.